#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:4
msgid "Contribution"
msgstr "贡献指南"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:6
msgid ""
"We welcome and appreciate contributions for the RPEP-SHOT library. Here "
"are the steps to contribute:"
msgstr "我们欢迎并感谢对 PREP-SHOT 库的贡献。贡献流程如下:"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:9
msgid "Development Process"
msgstr "开发流程"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:11
msgid "**Create an Issue**"
msgstr "**创建 Issue**"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:13
msgid ""
"If you find a bug or have an idea for an improvement or new feature, "
"please create an `issue <https://github.com/PREP-NexT/PREP-"
"SHOT/issues>`_."
msgstr ""
"如果你发现 bug 或有改进 / 新功能的想法,请创建 `issue <https://github.com/PREP-NexT/PREP-"
"SHOT/issues>`_。"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:15
msgid "**Fork the Repository**"
msgstr "**Fork 仓库**"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:17
msgid ""
"You can fork the `PREP-SHOT repository <https://github.com/PREP-NexT"
"/PREP-SHOT>`_ on GitHub."
msgstr ""
"你可以在 GitHub 上 fork `PREP-SHOT 仓库 <https://github.com/PREP-NexT/PREP-"
"SHOT>`_。"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:19
msgid "**Create a Branch**"
msgstr "**创建分支**"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:21
msgid ""
"Create a new branch in your forked repository and name the branch "
"according to the feature or fix you're working on."
msgstr "在你 fork 的仓库中创建新分支,并以正在处理的功能或修复命名。"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:23
msgid "**Commit Changes**"
msgstr "**提交修改**"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:25
msgid ""
"Make changes in your branch. Once you've made improvements or bug fixes "
"to the project, commit the changes with a meaningful commit message."
msgstr "在该分支中进行修改。完成改进或 bug 修复后,使用有意义的提交信息提交。"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:27
msgid ""
"**Run Tests** To execute all tests, navigate to the root directory of "
"PREP-SHOT and run:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:34
msgid "To check your code for PEP8 compliance, run:"
msgstr "检查代码是否符合 PEP8,运行:"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:41
msgid "**Start a Pull Request**"
msgstr "**发起 Pull Request**"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:43
msgid ""
"Open a `pull request <https://github.com/PREP-NexT/PREP-SHOT/pulls>`_ "
"from your forked repository to the main PREP-SHOT repository. Describe "
"your changes in the pull request."
msgstr ""
"从你 fork 的仓库向主 PREP-SHOT 仓库发起 `pull request <https://github.com/PREP-NexT"
"/PREP-SHOT/pulls>`_。在 PR 描述中说明你的修改。"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:45
msgid "**Code Review**"
msgstr "**代码评审**"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:47
msgid ""
"Maintainers of the PREP-SHOT project will review your code. They may ask "
"for changes or improvements before the code is merged into the main "
"codebase."
msgstr "PREP-SHOT 维护者会评审你的代码。他们可能会在代码合入主分支前要求改动或改进。"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:49
msgid ""
"Please ensure that you update tests as necessary when you're contributing"
" code, and follow the coding conventions established in the rest of the "
"project."
msgstr "贡献代码时请按需更新测试,并遵循项目其他部分既有的编码规范。"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:52
msgid "Building Documentation"
msgstr "构建文档"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:54
msgid ""
"The documentation is built using Sphinx. To build the documentation, you "
"need to install the required packages using the following command:"
msgstr "文档使用 Sphinx 构建。构建前请先用以下命令安装所需包:"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:60
msgid "You can build the documentation using the following command:"
msgstr "随后可用以下命令构建文档:"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:69
msgid "The documentation will be built in the `doc/build` directory."
msgstr "文档将构建在 `doc/build` 目录下。"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:72
msgid "Contributing Guidelines"
msgstr "贡献规范"

#: ../../source/Contribution.rst:74
msgid ""
"PREP-SHOT is written in Python and follows the PEP8 coding standard. "
"Please ensure that your code follows the PEP8 coding standard. You can "
"use the `Pylint <https://pylint.readthedocs.io/en/stable/>`_ tool to "
"check your code for PEP8 compliance."
msgstr ""
"PREP-SHOT 采用 Python 编写,遵循 PEP8 编码规范。请确保你的代码符合 PEP8。可使用 `Pylint "
"<https://pylint.readthedocs.io/en/stable/>`_ 工具检查 PEP8 合规性。"

